Package com.threerings.tudey.server

Interface Summary
TudeySceneManager.ActorObserver An interface for objects to notify when actors are added or removed.
TudeySceneManager.IntersectionSensor An interface for objects that should be notified when actors intersect them.
TudeySceneManager.Sensor Base interface for sensors.
TudeySceneManager.ShutdownObserver An interface for objects to notify when we shutdown.
TudeySceneManager.TickParticipant An interface for objects that take part in the server tick.
TudeySceneProvider Defines the server-side of the TudeySceneService.
 

Class Summary
ClientLiaison Handles interaction with a single client.
TudeySceneManager Manager for Tudey scenes.
TudeySceneMoveHandler Provides special handling for traversing portals.
TudeySceneRegistry Provides special handling for moving between Tudey scenes.
TudeyServer The base Tudey server.
TudeyServer.TudeyModule Configures dependencies needed by the Tudey services.
TudeyZoneMoveHandler Provides special handling for traversing portals and client-specific resolution.
TudeyZoneRegistry Provides special handling for moving between Tudey zones.
